            <h3 data-uuid="6f3a23e2ad314fa4931829cdeddcb2b2">Part 2: Write an Analytical Essay</h3>
            <h6 data-uuid="d7458262a6c949aa80e98b48f45c4ec2">Historical Context</h6>
            <p data-uuid="f7c7e8f5b0d8467db2e541c5726505c0">Following the French and Indian War, there was
                an increasing dissatisfaction between the colonists and Great Britain. In the
                1770s some colonial leaders became convinced that they could not avoid war with
                Britain. In 1776 the colonists declared their independence, but they would have
                to win a war against the British army to achieve their goal. The Patriots faced
                many hardships as the war raged on. Key American victories brought about turning points in the war. Americans won their independence from Great Britain
                in 1783 with the signing of the Treaty of Paris.</p>
            <h6 data-uuid="0d7c2b0228804a78b23b3cfff2f11739">Task</h6>
            <p data-uuid="bf785b7edea34f779c354299e6b63844">The American Revolution affected the colonists
                in different ways. The writings from the time show many different points of
                view. Write an analytical essay in which you discuss how Patriots from different
                backgrounds demonstrated their support for independence from Britain.</p>
            <p data-uuid="cc20ab5bfeec49ff95bfea9c6e97a953">Complete the following steps as you plan and compose your essay.</p>
            <ol data-uuid="51482b874d6141afb807f38d7fe8692c">
                <li data-uuid="5cb2990621c0408ebe443e85a921a0a0">
                    Review your notes and sources before you start writing.
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="090f252a84c446b08ab9e4e7b4823348">
                    Use at least <i>four</i> of the sources in Part 1, and develop the topic
                    with relevant, well-chosen text evidence from the documents.
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="4cd495d3c428419bb68a3c0ce760838e">
                    Cite specific text evidence from each of the sources in your
                    response.
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="ff7a86afb4cb4915adca97108e9c901a">
                    Plan your essay so that it includes an introduction,
                    several body paragraphs, and a concluding paragraph.</li>
                <li data-uuid="e7dc0bbd4c61471f89f1f961d92fd297">Organize your essay in a clear and logical way, and use relevant details to support your analysis.<br />
                </li>
                <li data-uuid="412ccf86830a4acda383f0412df045aa">Write a conclusion that sums up your ideas&#160;and supports the information you present.
                    <br />
                </li>
            </ol>
        </section>
